==== 市鎮 ====
{{main|市镇 (荷兰)|荷蘭市鎮政治|荷兰市镇列表}}

[[File:2019-NL-gemeenten-vol.jpg|300px]]
荷兰所有的[[荷兰省份|省份]]的下一级行政区划均为[[市镇_(荷兰)|市镇]]（{{lang-nl|gemeenten}}）。截至2019年1月，荷蘭共有355個市镇。[[市镇_(荷兰)|市镇]]是荷蘭的第二級行政區劃，也是荷蘭的第三層公共行政單位，次於[[荷蘭政治|中央政府]]和[[荷蘭省份|省分]]<ref name="adm_level">{{cite web |url=https://www.government.nl/topics/public-administration/provinces-municipalities-and-water-authorities |title=Provinces, municipalities and water authorities |work=government.nl |publisher=Government of the Netherlands |accessdate=2018-06-21 |language=en |archive-date=2018-06-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180621093142/https://www.government.nl/topics/public-administration/provinces-municipalities-and-water-authorities |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="OECD2007">{{cite book |title=OECD E-Government Studies: Netherlands 2007 |url=https://books.google.ca/books?id=5tlZ7HGd3ZoC&lpg=PP1&pg=PA40#v=onepage&q&f=false |page=40 |accessdate=2013-04-25 |date=28 May 2007 |publisher=OECD Publishing |location=Paris |isbn=978-92-64-03029-9 |language=en |archive-date=2017-05-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170510081451/https://books.google.ca/books?id=5tlZ7HGd3ZoC&lpg=PP1&pg=PA40#v=onepage&q&f=false |dead-url=no }}</ref>。市镇是由市長與市政委員所組成的{{link-nl|執行委員會 (荷蘭)|College van burgemeester en wethouders|執行委員會}}（college van burgemeester en wethouders，簡稱college van B&W或B&W），以及{{link-nl|市議會 (荷蘭)|Gemeenteraad|市議會}}（Gemeenteraad，簡稱GR）共同[[荷蘭市鎮政治|治理]]。特別市的市議會則被稱為{{link-nl|島議會|Eilandsraad (Caribisch Nederland)}}（eilandsraad）。市議會每四年選舉一次<ref name="4year_term">{{cite web |date = 2008 |title = Article 129. Chapter 7. The Constitution of the Kingdom of the Netherlands 2008 |publisher = Government of the Netherlands |website = government.nl |language = en |url = http://www.government.nl/issues/constitution-and-democracy/documents-and-publications/regulations/2012/10/18/the-constitution-of-the-kingdom-of-the-netherlands-2008.html |accessdate = 2013-04-08 |archive-date = 2013-03-20 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20130320094806/http://www.government.nl/issues/constitution-and-democracy/documents-and-publications/regulations/2012/10/18/the-constitution-of-the-kingdom-of-the-netherlands-2008.html |dead-url = no }}</ref>，市議會的成員數依所屬市的規模不等，少至九名，多至四十五名成員<ref name="act_no_members">{{cite act |title = Gemeentewet [Municipalities Act] |trans_title = Municipalities Act |number = 96 |article = 8 |language = nl |date = 1992-02-14 |url = http://wetten.overheid.nl/BWBR0005416/volledig/geldigheidsdatum_08-04-2013#TitelII_HoofdstukII_Artikel8 |accessdate = 2013-04-08 }} {{Wayback|url=http://wetten.overheid.nl/BWBR0005416/volledig/geldigheidsdatum_08-04-2013#TitelII_HoofdstukII_Artikel8 |date=20130605212044 }}</ref>。市議會是市的最高[[行政機構|行政機構]]，負責領導公共政策的走向。執行委員會由{{link-nl|市長 (荷蘭)|burgemeester|市長}}（burgemeester）和數名市政委員（wethouder）組成，握有市镇的執行權，負責執行政策的立法。市長六年一任，由中央政府指派，而市政委員則是由市議會選舉出來<ref name="act_mayor_term_and_aldermen">{{cite act |title = Gemeentewet [Municipalities Act] |trans_title = Municipalities Act |number = 96 |article = 61.1 and 35.1 |language = nl |date = 1992-02-14 |url = http://wetten.overheid.nl/BWBR0005416/volledig/geldigheidsdatum_08-04-2013 |accessdate = 2013-04-08 }} {{Wayback|url=http://wetten.overheid.nl/BWBR0005416/volledig/geldigheidsdatum_08-04-2013 |date=20130605212044 }}</ref>。市長除了負責維護市的公共秩序，在緊急危難時負有指揮權之外，其餘的治理任務可自由分配給市長和市政委員，因此具體的工作分配也因市而異<ref name="act_sp_muni" /><ref name="Elzinga2004Ch10">{{cite book|author1=A.H.M. Dölle|author2=D.J. Elzinga|author3=J.W.M. Engels|title=Handboek van het Nederlandse gemeenterecht|language=nl|trans-title=Manual of Dutch municipal law|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=yWu5dMARTt8C|accessdate=2013-04-25|date=2004-09-20|publisher=Kluwer|location=Alphen aan den Rijn|isbn=978-90-268-4169-9|chapter=De samenstelling van het college|trans-chapter=Members of the board|pages=233–252|archive-date=2013-06-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130608042620/http://books.google.com/books?id=yWu5dMARTt8C|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="muni_politics">{{cite web |url=http://www.government.nl/issues/municipalities-and-cities/municipal-government |title=Municipal government |work=government.nl |publisher=Government of the Netherlands |accessdate=2013-04-08 |language=en |archive-date=2015-05-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150518111000/http://www.government.nl/issues/municipalities-and-cities/municipal-government |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

荷蘭政府在陸續推行市的合併後，大幅減少了市鎮的數量，目前大約是自十九世紀中期行政區劃劃定以來的三分之一。市鎮又可因行政或統計的需求，被非正式地劃分為「社區」（wijken）和「鄰里」（buurten）等地區。

==== 公共实体（加勒比海部分） ====
{{main|荷蘭加勒比區}}
荷蘭除本土12个省外，另外在[[加勒比海|加勒比海]]有[[博奈尔|博奈尔]]、[[圣尤斯特歇斯|圣尤斯特歇斯]]、[[萨巴|萨巴]]三个直属荷兰的三個特別行政區（{{lang-nl|''Bijzondere gemeenten''}}），依荷蘭法律定義為{{link-nl|公共实体 (荷兰)|Openbaar lichaam|公共实体}}，合稱[[荷蘭加勒比區|荷蘭加勒比區]]，並不隸屬於任何省分<ref name="act_sp_muni">{{cite act |title = Wet openbare lichamen Bonaire, Sint Eustatius en Saba |trans_title=Public bodies act Bonaire, Sint Eustatius and Saba |number = 345 |language = nl |date = 10 October 2010 |url = http://wetten.overheid.nl/BWBR0028142/ |accessdate = 2013-04-05}}</ref>，擁有一般荷蘭本土[[荷兰市镇政治|市政府功能]]。各島政府由一名市長（{{lang-nl|''gezaghebber''}}）及市內閣（{{lang-nl|''bestuurscollege''}}）組成，向各島公民選出的{{tsl|en|Island council (Netherlands)|島議會}}（{{lang-nl|''eilandsraad''}}）問責。荷兰加勒比区國家辦公室（{{lang-nl|''Rijksdienst Caribisch Nederland''}}）則負責稅務、治安、入出境、教育、社會福利。

